              " 'alice,) well, i hardly know--no more, thank ye; im better now--but im',\n",
              " 'a deal too flustered to tell you--all i know is, something comes at me',\n",
              " 'like a jack-in-the-box, and up i goes like a sky-rocket!',\n",
